metadata.description:
memento mori ¢

memento mori literally means "Remember you must die".

Your life is represented by a jar of pennies. Every week is represented by a single penny. 

How have you spent them? Will any of your pennies have a lasting impact? How many pennies do you have left? 

Do you stop to smell the roses? Do you take the time to explore? Do you spend your pennies on you; or, on others?

How much are your pennies worth?
